# DataTidy19RodoVaccComp

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of DataTidy19RodoVaccComp is to process the data for the Rodo (2019) vaccine comparison paper.

## Installation

You can install the development version of DataTidy19RodoVaccComp from [GitHub](https://github.com/) with:

``` r
# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("SATVILab/DataTidy19RodoVaccComp")
```
